{"type": "article", "id": 22620, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-02-22T08:22:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 2976, "name": "灯饰"}, {"id": 23744, "name": "有所"}, {"id": 23745, "name": "SPIN-R"}, {"id": 23746, "name": "Goat Story"}, {"id": 23747, "name": "一融设计"}, {"id": 23748, "name": "Kristine Five Melvær"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122221GlbaYqke6pBj8xUQ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>The Vava stool by Kristine Five Melvær </h2>\n<p>这是挪威设计师 Kristine Five Melvær 在斯德哥尔摩家具展上展出的椅子。圆形座位下的椅腿像是三个大波浪弧线，首尾相连，它实际将接口隐藏了起来。从不同角度看，3 个支撑结构则形成不同的几何造型，而连贯的结构既具有装饰性，也可以使得椅子显得简单轻盈。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142147xQ8b7sT2VLKo0AvN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061421471RALUX9HGExgQekJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142148j7oVr3a5HGIBMbg0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142148an9KEpVvAWbwL7Ik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142149YAce10LwChDRsKaG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>布丁沙发 by 有所</h2>\n<p>这是有所品牌推出的一款想让人联想到“布丁”的沙发，亮丽的黄色配合有些拟人化的设计让沙发显得甜美可爱。两边的扶手和沙发上的垫子都是圆柱形的，偶尔采用棕色的仿皮面料作为反差，增加了光泽感。细木腿的使用也突出了沙发的主体，显得柔软舒适。另有一款绿色的“抹茶布丁”，售价 2850 元，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1-c.w5003-11731905043.4.fBw1zJ&amp;id=521830547590&amp;scene=taobao_shop\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142149iHR2dxlFf3OQzrJ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061421508FW3NQKRfI2Ybwum.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142150PqFXc3ANU4EbBM89.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142150OYxCJBZqNzkAhdE7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061421516rYZJRxQ7ivp8BeS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>水边故事系列 by HDK</h2>\n<p>这是来自瑞典哥特堡大学设计工艺学院（HDK）的学生设计的家具系列，他们以水边的故事（stories by the water）为主题。圆桌  Sophie hardy 用 65 层纸制作，边缘有彩色的立体波浪，模拟出水纹的感觉。另有一款木质屏风上做出了凹凸感，在光影下也有水纹的效果。还有一款柜子上覆盖有大理石图案，搭配以拱形的结构，线条柔和有如水光。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061421517fiWqhmuIrTnHLXo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80806846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142152bCFRUaNe4pvStcfW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77383863\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142152107oWJbexwZ4uGNS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31173594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142153cwL7JIBuqRnjpWKN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.21271394\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142154cXP5L9aTiIpxgb8u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05012225\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Tittle Light by SPIN-R</h2>\n<p>这是美国设计工作室 SPIN-R 带来的一款方形的 LED 灯 Tittle，它含有 512 个小的节点，可以与智能手机相连来控制灯的颜色、亮度以及变化的模式，产生出类似霓虹灯的效果。灯体小巧而色彩绚丽，是调节气氛的小工具。产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/tittle-light-the-captivating-3d-led-smart-lamp#/\">这里是众筹链接</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142154IdG8eiWsHJD6TSlK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142155yFZ9BmI52TcgHKNu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142155Lefrj497amoGU1My.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142156JfhGpPaNtsxndb8M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142156giOBAGj4zsLQSm8W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>G-Drip coffee by Goat Story</h2>\n<p>这是一款滴漏式的咖啡装置设计，设计团队 Goat Story 采用了一个实验室风格。它的主体结构是一个很简单的木制管道，有金属的关节接口，从上至下在不同的维度进行直角转折，最后在地上形成半包围的结构作为支撑，非常简洁。滴过后的咖啡汁液直接装进了圆锥玻璃瓶里，上面有清晰的刻度标示。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142157QECNuSyfmWn61ZBb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142157DEPbH7fSq34VNgd9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142157h73MPEN5W9Ydor2f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142158wFIlrAT67VPtRCjU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061421581LgCk4quFjoNUlbY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>          </p>\n<h2>Pocket Penguins by Penguins</h2>\n<p>企鹅出版计划在今年 5 月出一套 20 Pocket Penguins，沿用“小黑书”（ LBC ）的版式，回归复古的纯色封面。不同的是这些书的封面采用了丰富的颜色，它们代表了不同的语言，橄榄绿代表德语，红色代表俄罗斯语，深蓝色代表法语......可以组成一个色彩丰富的调色板，非常清新。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061421594IT0aZ2OG9BfcFyz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061421596rpsPMBU8fmzcVAQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142200db2Bm8TqOUADCEer.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142200OK0gdvu5k4poAsqQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.11125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142201DtEOx3rBTuMdsz6m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1475\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142201IJdNfLuecp62tqHE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}